2012-12-12 Sasa Ostrouska <saxa@droplinegnome.org>

	3.6_r4104
	* Updated the installer source to the svn checkout source
	possibly this becomes the alpha installer for both archs.
	* From now on we will use in alpha , beta , and RC phases 
	the following nameing scheme for the sources of the installer
	<$MAJ_VER>.<$MIN_VER>_<svn revision nr.> and when we get the 
	thing sorted out and tagged then we use only the first part
	with <$MAJ_VER>.<$MIN_VER> .

